article:
Qatari citizens do not need a visa to enter other member states of the GCC. They
also have the right to take up jobs in those countries. Similarly, citizens of
other GCC states do not need a visa to enter Qatar. Also, Qatari citizens do not
need a visa to enter many member states of the Arab League.

According to the "Henley Visa Restrictions Index 2012", holders of a Qatari
passport can visit 65 countries visa-free or with visa on arrival.
